      public ExecutorService.ExecutorConfig setAllowCoreThreadTimeout(boolean allowCoreThreadTimeout)
      Allows timing out of core threads. Good to set this for non-critical thread pools for release of unused resources. Refer to ThreadPoolExecutor.allowCoreThreadTimeOut(boolean) for additional details.
